{"tid":1343482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"石鏡泉「煽惑他人煽惑公眾妨擾」","createTime":"2019-07-21T18:50:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T11:39:07.000Z","uid":263659,"like":185,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"7d4a96251d8d95ce418fd627d5d9e8ab118f01fc","tid":1343482,"uid":263659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:50:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">7月20日</span></strong><br />\n經濟日報副社長石鏡泉表示... 市民要學習元朗、深水埗的街坊，要以「力」，而非「暴力」去解決問題。他又呼籲，每個人都應該<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">自備藤條或膠水喉通</span></span></strong>來<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">「教仔」</span></span></strong>：「我哋要用力，唔要暴，藤條打仔點算暴呢？」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/22251/%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E9%AB%98%E6%B0%B8%E6%96%87-%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-22251/ko-wingman\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F22251%2F%25E5%25AE%2588%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%25B0%25B8%25E6%2596%2587-%25E7%258D%25A8%25E7%25AB%258B%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5-22251%2Fko-wingman&d=0ZQOgT4XWRiGBLzCIZSXcitC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=0fba2fc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/22251/%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E9%AB%98%E6%B0%B8%E6%96%87-%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-22251/ko-wingman</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">7月21日</span></strong><br />\n晚上11時左右，在元朗站有疑似黑社會人士衝入車廂尾，並<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">用粗藤條及竹棍毆打乘客</span></span></strong>，且不分上衫顏色、男女均照打。同時，大堂充斥叫囂聲，可見血漬及<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">「保衛家園」</span></span></strong>的示威牌。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/354605/%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97-%E5%89%8Dtvb%E4%B8%BB%E6%92%AD%E6%9F%B3%E4%BF%8A%E6%B1%9F%E9%81%AD%E6%89%93%E8%87%B3%E8%A1%80%E6%B5%81%E6%8A%AB%E9%